{
  "stem": "9963.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, to the funeral.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because after the funeral, I went back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that camp, we were about seven months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at that camp what happened, what-- we know already what it will happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, the-- the Germans walk away their cities, you know, to the ghettos-- little towns, they put to the bigger city where they made ghettos.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we know the-- I personally know exactly which city will be evacuated and when.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] As I got to know about four months before our city would be evacuated, exactly the date and everything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I've mentioned it before, that I had the contact with the underground and they let me know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was Polish name like first names, like John, Robert.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Things, you know-- not-- didn't-- it was everything on a personal basis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] When I got to know this, at that camp was an older gentleman.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had four sons in that camp-- a father and four sons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was all the time kept in contact with that other gentleman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a very little man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was very, very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I see to it that one of his sons will be the eldest in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, what he was saying about barracks, take care of the barracks, sweep the barracks, keep it clean.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was the eldest, and keep his father for his helper, so that the father wouldn't have to go out to work the hard labor.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when I seen the things like that, you know-- I was always working for people, you know, and always, you know, was very beloved and very respected.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
